trans-unit.source: Provides a reusable <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.UserControl" /> object for editing <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection" /> objects.
trans-unit.target: Proporciona un objeto <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.UserControl" /> reutilizables para editar los objetos <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterCollectionEditor> class provides a user interface for editing the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter> elements of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection> objects that are referenced by several different properties of controls at design time.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterCollectionEditor> clase proporciona una interfaz de usuario para editar la <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter> elementos de <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection> objetos que se hace referencia a varias propiedades de controles en tiempo de diseño.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl> class encapsulates most of the functionality of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterCollectionEditor>.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl> clase encapsula la mayoría de las funciones de la <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterCollectionEditor>.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterCollectionEditor> consists of an enclosing form that holds the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl>, and **OK** and **Cancel** buttons.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterCollectionEditor> consta de un formulario envolvente que contiene el <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl>, y **Aceptar** y **cancelar** botones.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.AddParameters%2A> method adds an array of existing parameters to the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl>.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.AddParameters%2A> método agrega una matriz de parámetros existentes a la <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl>.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.ClearParameters%2A> method removes all parameters from the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl>.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.ClearParameters%2A> método quita todos los parámetros de la <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl>.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.GetParameters%2A> method gets all parameters from the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl>.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.GetParameters%2A> método obtiene todos los parámetros de la <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl>.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.SetAllowCollectionChanges%2A> method controls whether additions and deletions can be made to the parameters in the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl>.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.SetAllowCollectionChanges%2A> método controla si se pueden realizar adiciones y eliminaciones a los parámetros de la <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl>.

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.IServiceProvider" /> interface to the current design host, such as [!INCLUDE[vsprvslong](~/includes/vsprvslong-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: Interfaz <see cref="T:System.IServiceProvider" /> para el host de diseño actual, como [!INCLUDE[vsprvslong](~/includes/vsprvslong-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl" /> class using the specified <see cref="T:System.IServiceProvider" />.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa una nueva instancia de la clase <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl" /> utilizando la clase <see cref="T:System.IServiceProvider" /> especificada.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.%23ctor%2A> constructor initializes the component controls of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl> object, initializes UI elements, connects events for the individual component editors, and adds the component editors to the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Controls%2A> collection for the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl>.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.%23ctor%2A> constructor inicializa los controles de componente de la <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl> objeto, inicializa los elementos de interfaz de usuario, conecta los eventos para los editores de componentes individuales y agrega los editores de componentes para la <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Controls%2A> colección para el <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl>.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter" /> array of existing parameters to add to the editor.
trans-unit.target: Matriz <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter" /> de los parámetros existentes que se van a agregar al editor.

trans-unit.source: Adds an array of existing parameters to the editor.
trans-unit.target: Agrega una matriz de parámetros existentes al editor.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.AddParameters%2A> method adds the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter> elements of `parameters` to the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListView> control in the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl> object.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.AddParameters%2A> método agrega la <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter> elementos de `parameters` a la <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListView> controlar en el <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl> objeto.

trans-unit.source: If there is more than one <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter> element, the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.AddParameters%2A> selects the first one in the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListView>.
trans-unit.target: Si hay más de un <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter> elemento, el <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.AddParameters%2A> selecciona la primera de ellas en el <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListView>.

trans-unit.source: Then the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.AddParameters%2A> refreshes the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListView> control and raises the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection.ParametersChanged> event.
trans-unit.target: La <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.AddParameters%2A> actualiza el <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListView> control y genera el <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection.ParametersChanged> eventos.

trans-unit.source: Removes all parameters from the editor.
trans-unit.target: Quita todos los parámetros del editor.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.ClearParameters%2A> method removes the parameters from the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListView> control in the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl> object.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.ClearParameters%2A> método quita los parámetros de la <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListView> controlar en el <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl> objeto.

trans-unit.source: Then the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.ClearParameters%2A> refreshes the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListView> control and raises the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection.ParametersChanged> event.
trans-unit.target: La <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.ClearParameters%2A> actualiza el <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListView> control y genera el <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection.ParametersChanged> eventos.

trans-unit.source: Gets all parameters from the editor.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene todos los parámetros del editor.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter" /> array of all parameters from the editor.
trans-unit.target: Una matriz <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter" /> de todos los parámetros del editor.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.GetParameters%2A> method populates a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter> array with all parameters from the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListView> control in the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl>.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.GetParameters%2A> método rellena una <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter> matriz con todos los parámetros de la <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListView> controlar en el <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl>.

trans-unit.source: The source of the event.
trans-unit.target: Origen del evento.

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.EventArgs" /> object that contains the event data.
trans-unit.target: Objeto <see cref="T:System.EventArgs" /> que contiene los datos del evento.

trans-unit.source: Raises the <see cref="E:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.ParametersChanged" /> event when the state of a parameter in the editor changes.
trans-unit.target: Genera el evento <see cref="E:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.ParametersChanged" /> cuando cambia el estado de un parámetro en el editor.

trans-unit.source: Occurs when any parameter or one of the parameter's properties is changed.
trans-unit.target: Se produce cuando cambia cualquier parámetro o una de sus propiedades.

trans-unit.source: Returns a value indicating whether all the parameters in the editor are configured.
trans-unit.target: Devuelve un valor que indica si están configurados todos los parámetros del editor.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if all parameters in the editor are fully configured; otherwise <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: Es <see langword="true" /> si todos los parámetros del editor están configurados totalmente; de lo contrario, es <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Boolean" /> that indicates whether additions and deletions can be made to the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection" /> being edited.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Boolean" /> que indica si se pueden realizar adiciones y eliminaciones en <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection" /> que se está editando.

trans-unit.source: Controls whether additions and deletions can be made to the values in the editor.
trans-unit.target: Controla si se pueden agregar y eliminar valores del editor.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.SetAllowCollectionChanges%2A> method controls whether additions and deletions can be made to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection> element in the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl> object.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.SetAllowCollectionChanges%2A> método controla si se pueden realizar adiciones y eliminaciones en el <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection> elemento en el <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl> objeto.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.SetAllowCollectionChanges%2A> enables or disables the Up, Down, Add, and Delete buttons but it does not affect the editing of individual <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter> elements.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.SetAllowCollectionChanges%2A> habilita o deshabilita los arriba, abajo, agregar y eliminar botones pero no afecta a la edición de persona <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter> elementos.

trans-unit.source: Provides metadata for the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Proporciona los metadatos de la clase <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl" />.

trans-unit.source: A type descriptor provider object.
trans-unit.target: Objeto de proveedor del descriptor de tipos.
